  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that in the annals of the Further East, it is believed that the <a href=\"/index.php/Long_Night\" title=\"Long Night\">Long Night</a> was caused by the <a href=\"/index.php/Blood_Betrayal\" title=\"Blood Betrayal\">Blood Betrayal</a>, when the <a href=\"/index.php/Bloodstone_Emperor\" title=\"Bloodstone Emperor\">Bloodstone Emperor</a> slew the <a href=\"/index.php/Amethyst_Empress\" title=\"Amethyst Empress\">Amethyst Empress</a>?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/145&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Bones and Beyond: Yi Ti.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403205153\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 97/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8542/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 408/2097152 byte